{"tid":1479234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰最後有無交罷工名單畀北京？","createTime":"2019-08-16T21:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:56:25.000Z","uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef16da4a02f639150f4b801ccd94b27fade9f610","tid":1479234,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T21:50:57.000Z","msg":"點解我見到有人爆國泰CEO為咗保護員工而辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實如果接手嗰個奶共<br />\n罷工班友一樣gg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c0fbfc219ed5366544152bed13d9df16b35a07","tid":1479234,"uid":194745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"國泰不嬲好嘅只係啲機師空姐，國泰航空間公司同管理層不嬲對機師空姐極差，只因有機師空姐工會幫佢哋。啲管理層只是吸血蛀米大蟲，吸盡機師同空姐的工作成果。<br />\n<br />\n啲管理層炒燃油對沖蝕錢，就搵員工裁員找數。自己亂駛錢大花筒就刻薄空姐，減航班人手加座位。<br />\n<br />\n大家要分開公司同員工，pacific place啲員工幫手，唔代表太古幫手。太古不嬲都是奶共㗎<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啲管理層已經將員工名單交給民航局，嗰啲示過威表過態嘅黃絲空姐機師冇得飛越中國領空，好快會被迫走，成間公司上上下下管理層機師空姐都會係藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n太古一早已經奶共，當初自願將國泰股權交出媚共自保，繼續揾銀。反而怡和遷冊撤出香港。</span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/86420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F86420&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75S%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=552c155e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/86420</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新CEO 鄧生來自港機工程，一早紮根厦門，一定好識做</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n去台灣，長榮/中華<br />\n<br />\n去日本， JAL ANA PEACH<br />\n<br />\n去歐洲 英航，三寶, virgin Air France lufthansa<br />\n<br />\n去澳洲 virgin qantas<br />\n<br />\n去美國 AA United<br />\n<br />\n去中國  冇計 國泰港龍"}]}